PrecisEnactment of the RADIOCOMMUNICATION ACT (SUBSECTION 4(1) AND PARAGRAPH 9(1)(b)) EXEMPTION ORDER (SECURITY AND SAFETY, INTERNATIONAL RELATIONS AND NATIONAL DEFENCE), NO. 2002-1 - which exempts the RCMP and the Canadian Forces from the application of the Act with respect to interfering with radiocommunication signals during the G8 Summit being held in Kananaskis.

Enactment of the RADIOCOMMUNICATION ACT (SUBSECTION 4(1) AND PARAGRAPH
9(1)(b)) EXEMPTION ORDER (SECURITY AND SAFETY, INTERNATIONAL RELATIONS AND
NATIONAL DEFENCE), NO. 2002-1 -  which exempts the RCMP and the Canadian
